modules.description: Splits strings based on custom delimiters and returns lists of substrings. Processes strings with options for trimming whitespace and handling empty elements. Useful for parsing log lines, CSV data, and command-line arguments.

Provides string manipulation functions such as splitting with or without preserving separators, trimming left-side characters, and replacing patterns. Works with strings, character lists, arrays, and character ranges. Used for parsing log lines by splitting on delimiters, sanitizing input by trimming unwanted characters, and modifying strings with pattern replacements.
